product_name: Ahnu Jackie Reptile Embossed Shoes - Women's
long_description: Celebrating the modern day "Jackie of all trades", the Ahnu Jackie Reptile Embossed shoes will go anywhere with you, all day long. Leather uppers offer soft, pliable wear in sophisticated style you can take to the office or out to dinner on the town. Microfiber suede liners wick moisture away to keep feet dry and comfortable; antimicrobial treatment discourages odors. Polyurethane midsoles supply lightweight cushion for all-day walking comfort. Nylon shanks offer arch support so your feet won't tire as quickly. Heel stabilizers boost support throughout your walking stride. Ahnu Jackie Reptile Embossed shoes feature nonmarking rubber outsoles for reliable traction on a variety of surfaces.
